		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_BUILDINGS_MONDSTADT_WINDMILL_TEXT">
			<Text>Mondstadt's Windmills are located in the city of Mondstadt in the World of Teyvat. Their size may vary and are very useful in the daily life of the inhabitants of the city. Legend has it that the Mondstadt's Windmills represent every step that Barbatros, the Anemo Archon, took when the city was founded. They represent an undisputed symbol of the city and its inhabitants are very proud of them. On the symbol of Mondstadt, one of its mills is represented there.</Text>
